Package com.api.synco.module.user.domain.service

Class UserService

java.lang.Object
com.api.synco.module.user.domain.service.UserService
@Service public class UserService extends Object
Domain service for user management operations.

This service coordinates user-related business operations by delegating to appropriate use cases and handling the mapping between domain entities and DTOs.

Responsibilities:

  • User creation with validation
  • User deletion with permission checks
  • User profile editing
  • User retrieval by ID
  • Paginated user listing with filters

    • getAll

      public List<UserGetResponse> getAll(String name, String email, RoleUser roleUser, Instant createAt, Instant updateAt, int pageNumber, int pageSize)
      Retrieves a paginated list of users with optional filters.
      Parameters:
      name - filter by name containing this value (optional)
      email - filter by email containing this value (optional)
      roleUser - filter by user role (optional)
      createAt - filter users created from this date onwards (optional)
      updateAt - filter users updated up to this date (optional)
      pageNumber - the page number to retrieve (0-based)
      pageSize - the number of users per page
      Returns:
      a list of users matching the criteria
